WEBVTT

00:11.395 --> 00:14.465
<i>I want to tell you about a man
I once knew.</i>

00:17.501 --> 00:22.690
<i>He lived in a land so beautiful
and white and silent,</i>

00:22.790 --> 00:25.943
<i>that if you scraped
a harpoon on the ice,</i>

00:26.043 --> 00:28.813
<i>you could hear it for miles and miles.</i>

